name: Handcrafted Teak Wood Dining Table
description: This dining table is made from high-quality teak wood and features intricate hand-carved designs. It comfortably seats six and adds a touch of elegance to any dining room.

name: Wooden Elephant Sculpture
description: A beautiful wooden sculpture of an elephant, handcrafted from solid rosewood. It stands 12 inches tall and serves as a stunning decorative piece for any room.

name: Hand-carved Wooden Wall Clock
description: This unique wall clock is crafted from sustainable mango wood and features intricate hand-carved details. It adds a rustic charm to any home decor.

name: Wooden Photo Frame Set
description: A set of three wooden photo frames made from reclaimed oak wood. These frames add a vintage touch to your photos and complement any interior style.

name: Handcrafted Bamboo Cutting Board
description: This bamboo cutting board is eco-friendly and durable, perfect for everyday use in the kitchen. It is resistant to knife marks and easy to clean.

name: Wooden Salad Bowl Set
description: A set of two wooden salad bowls made from acacia wood. These bowls are perfect for serving salads, fruits, or snacks and add a natural touch to your table.

name: Jute Rope Wall Hanging
description: A decorative wall hanging made from natural jute rope. It adds a bohemian touch to any room and is perfect for hanging plants, photos, or ornaments.

name: Jute Cushion Cover Set
description: A set of two cushion covers made from soft jute fabric. These covers feature intricate woven patterns and add warmth and texture to your living space.

name: Jute Placemat Set
description: A set of four placemats made from natural jute fibers. These placemats protect your dining table from heat and spills while adding a rustic charm to your table setting.

name: Jute Pot Holder
description: A jute pot holder with a cotton lining, perfect for handling hot pots and pans in the kitchen. It features a loop for easy hanging when not in use.

name: Wood and Jute Statement Necklace
description: A unique statement necklace featuring wooden beads and jute accents. It adds a touch of natural beauty to any outfit and is perfect for boho-inspired looks.

name: Jute Wrapped Wooden Bangle Set
description: A set of three wooden bangles wrapped in colorful jute threads. These bangles add a pop of color and texture to your accessory collection.
